      <title>Vanguard 首次在西班牙招聘员工，旨在促进当地业务发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/vanguard-aims-to-grow-in-spain-with-its-first-hire-in-the-country</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球第二大资产管理公司先锋集团 (Vanguard Group Inc.) 计划在西班牙首次招聘员工，该公司正努力在西班牙发展业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/vanguard-aims-to-grow-in-spain-with-its-first-hire-in-the-country</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 14:42:43 GMT</pubDate>
