      <title>Stora 计划投资 1 亿欧元开发木质电池</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/stora-enso-hel-sterv-invests-in-lignin-ev-batteries-ceo-hans-sohlstrom-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据斯道拉恩索公司首席执行官称，斯道拉恩索公司正准备投资约 1 亿欧元（1.1 亿美元）用于一项开创性项目，将木材用于电动汽车电池，并为目前在中国生产的零部件提供替代品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/stora-enso-hel-sterv-invests-in-lignin-ev-batteries-ceo-hans-sohlstrom-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:52:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
